All epics created and wired. Here's the summary:

## Cycle 4 Polish Epics

All 4 reviewers crashed/returned empty. I conducted a manual audit across audio engine, UI controls, interactive views, accessibility, state management, and design tokens. Found 50+ specific issues.

**Execution order:**

**Phase 1 (parallel):**
- `ist` (P1) -- QA browser verification (ground truth before fixing)
- `264` (P1) -- Audio engine safety (feedback loops, timer drift, bounce, denormals)
- `2ri` (P1) -- Missing interactive features (ADSR viz, oscilloscope, presets, drag-to-arrange, effects reorder, velocity editing)

**Phase 2 (after QA):**
- `nq5` (P1) -- Accessibility & reduced motion (prefers-reduced-motion, ARIA, headings, focus)
- `nq7` (P2) -- Micro-interactions & visual polish (transitions, hover states, cursor feedback)
- `y4t` (P2) -- State persistence + design token migration (race conditions, orphaned blobs, hardcoded values)

